" =============================================================================
" File    : plugins/commentary.vim
" Brief   : Comments keybinds.
" Plugin  : https://github.com/tpope/vim-commentary
" NOTE    : gc, gcc, etc are added automatically.
" =============================================================================
Plug 'tpope/vim-commentary'

" -- KeyMaps ------------------------------------------------------------------

" Toggle comment on the current paragraph
nmap gbc vipgc